commit.message:
S/390: Cleanup builtin types file

gcc/ChangeLog:

2019-03-25  Andreas Krebbel  <krebbel@linux.ibm.com>

	* config/s390/s390-builtin-types.def: Remove few unused types and
	fix sort order for others.

From-SVN: r269909
